==Korean==
===Verb===
'''나누다''' ''na.nu.da''
#to [[divide]] (into pieces), to split up
#:빵을 두 동강으로 '''나누다'''. (''Bbang-eul du donggang-euro '''nanuda''''') '''Divide''' bread into two pieces.
#(mathematics) to divide
#to [[share]]
#:술을 한 잔 '''나누다'''. (''suleul han jan nanuda'') '''Share''' a glass of wine.
#:이야기를 즐겁게 '''나누다'''. (Iyagireul jeulgeopke nanuda) Enjoy '''sharing''' stories. [[ko:나누다]]
